name: R5-ParameterDefinition-R4-ParameterDefinition
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R5 ParameterDefinition into FHIR R4

element.display: Definition of a parameter to a module

target.display: Definition of a parameter to a module
target.comment: R5 `ParameterDefinition` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition`

element.display: A brief description of the parameter

target.display: A brief description of the parameter
target.comment: R5 `ParameterDefinition.documentation` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.documentation`
R5 `ParameterDefinition.extension` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.extension`
R5 `ParameterDefinition.id` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.id`
R5 `ParameterDefinition.max` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.max`
R5 `ParameterDefinition.min` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.min`

element.display: Name used to access the parameter value

target.display: Name used to access the parameter value
target.comment: R5 `ParameterDefinition.name` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.name`

element.display: What profile the value is expected to be

target.display: What profile the value is expected to be
target.comment: R5 `ParameterDefinition.profile` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.profile`

R5 `ParameterDefinition.type` maps as RelatedTo to R4 `ParameterDefinition.type` - (type failed to compare required binding of http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/fhir-types|5.0.0 and http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/all-types|4.0.1); type has change due to type change: R5 `type` `code` maps as RelatedTo for R4 `type`

R5 `ParameterDefinition.use` maps as Equivalent to R4 `ParameterDefinition.use` - use has compatible required binding for code type: http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/operation-parameter-use|5.0.0 and http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/operation-parameter-use|4.0.1 (Equivalent)
